  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they collected them and put them in to working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were treated very badly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was by the Hungarians, and the people who were above them were the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the guards, and they were the bosses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very, very, very-- that was the first humiliating part of the town when that happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, these gypsies [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] weren't educated or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they kind of took revenge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Here were these so-called rich people who-- whom we were always under or-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and now we could take revenge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like you had an old-- we had an old doctor, a little fat, old man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to make him carry two sacks at a time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You will carry it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if not, they hit him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, it-- it was very humiliating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the first of the down, the road down, the way down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were there for a few months and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
